description:
This course explores an aspect of the 19th-Century novel intensively; specific course topics will vary from year to year. 

See the English Department's website at www.english.upenn.edu for a description of the current offerings.
name: TPCS 19TH-CENTURY NOVEL: The Good Life:  Novels, Biographies, and the 19th Century Imagination
